# Test Data

This directory contains real ethoscope database files for testing.

## test_ethoscope.db

- **Source**: Ethoscope 070 from July 10, 2025
- **Size**: 6.2MB
- **ROIs**: 20 ROIs (ROI_1 through ROI_20)
- **Data points**: ~20k rows per ROI
- **Original path**: `/mnt/ethoscope_data/results/070b51f413f540de855a4cbd74b0a9a5/ETHOSCOPE_070/2025-07-10_08-54-16/2025-07-10_08-54-16_070b51f413f540de855a4cbd74b0a9a5.db`

This database provides realistic data for integration testing of ethoscopy data loading and analysis functions.
